data.description: Welcome to Monterey Bay!  A pet friendly townhome community conveniently located with easy access to 95 from both the north and south and only a half mile north of Delray's Atlantic Ave.  This 3 bed 2.5 bath has been lovingly updated by the current owners.  Features include new AC, luxury vinyl wood plank throughout, living room accent wall, new master shower, as well as many other touches.  This unit is from the 2013 build in Monterey Bay which means you enjoy complete impact glass.  Come see what makes this neighborhood so highly sought after.
